<h2>I. Why Ad Creative is the Core Competitive Advantage in Meta Marketing</h2>
<p>In the Meta advertising ecosystem, the importance of creative cannot be overstated. According to Meta's official data, under identical targeting conditions, high-quality creatives can achieve 3-5x higher click-through rates (CTR) compared to poor creatives, with cost per acquisition (CPA) reduced by 40%-60%.</p>
<p>More critically, <strong>creative determines the advertising lifecycle</strong>. An excellent creative can maintain stable ROI while running continuously for 6-12 months, while poor creatives typically experience significant performance decay (Creative Fatigue) within 3-5 days.</p>
<h3>1.1 The Role of Creative at Each Funnel Stage</h3>
