<h3>4.2 Identifying and Addressing Creative Fatigue</h3>
<p><strong>Warning indicators</strong>:<br />
- Same creative's CTR drops by more than 15%<br />
- CPM starts rising<br />
- Conversion costs increase by more than 20%</p>
<p><strong>Response strategies</strong>:<br />
1. Prepare creative library in advance, maintain 2-3 new creatives online weekly<br />
2. Use Dynamic Creative feature to automatically combine creative elements<br />
3. Establish creative lifecycle management to replace declining creatives timely</p>
