<h2>V. Common Mistakes and Avoidance Guide</h2>
<h3>5.1 Top 10 Creative Design禁忌</h3>
<ol>
<li><strong>Too much text</strong>: Text exceeding 20% of the visual significantly reduces engagement</li>
<li><strong>Oversized logo</strong>: Logo centered on the image gives a "hard sell" impression</li>
<li><strong>Low-resolution images</strong>: Blurry/stretched images severely damage brand trust</li>
<li><strong>Product-only images</strong>: Lack of scenario and emotional resonance leads to low CTR</li>
<li><strong>False exaggeration</strong>: Overpromising without delivery damages brand reputation</li>
<li><strong>Ignoring mobile optimization</strong>: Creatives not optimized for mobile lose 40%+ conversions</li>
<li><strong>Unclear CTA</strong>: Users don't know what to do next</li>
<li><strong>Slow loading</strong>: Over 3-second load times cause 53% user drop-off</li>
<li><strong>Mismatch with landing page</strong>: Promises in creative don't match landing page content</li>
<li><strong>Over-relying on templates</strong>: "Cookie-cutter" creatives lack differentiation and cause fatigue</li>
</ol>
<h3>5.2 Industry-Specific Creative Recommendations</h3>
