<td>Beautiful game graphics + character showcase + download CTA</td>
<td>Avoid low-quality screenshots</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Finance</td>
<td>Professional feel + data backing + security promises</td>
<td>Avoid exaggerated returns</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Tools/App</td>
<td>Feature demos + efficiency comparisons + clean UI</td>
<td>Avoid overly complex interfaces</td>
</tr>
<tr>
